{"tid":2286671,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【泰國示威】逾千人再上街 掛白布表訴求 背對泰王車隊抗議","createTime":"2020-11-15T07:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T08:40:13.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b6807fffac4e08b1a7306a9403458437eaa0373e","tid":2286671,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T07:36:42.000Z","msg":"泰國反政府示威已持續三個多月，示威者昨日（14日）再在首都曼谷民主紀念碑附近舉行大規模集會，將寫有訴求的大幅白布掛上民主紀念碑。期間，泰王哇集拉隆功經過集會地點，示威者背對車隊，又舉起三指禮以示抗議。<br />\n<br />\n昨日的集會由 Bad Students、Free Women 及 Mob Fest 三個團體聯合發起，示威者在集會上高叫口號，又播放嘲弄政府的歌曲。主辦方帶來了一條 30 平方米的白色大布，邀請示威者寫上自己的訴求，包括要求總理巴育下台及修改憲法等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%83%E4%BA%BA%E5%86%8D%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%97-%E6%8E%9B%E7%99%BD%E5%B8%83%E8%A1%A8%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82-%E8%83%8C%E5%B0%8D%E6%B3%B0%E7%8E%8B%E8%BB%8A%E9%9A%8A%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581-%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%258D%2583%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2586%258D%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A1%2597-%25E6%258E%259B%25E7%2599%25BD%25E5%25B8%2583%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582-%25E8%2583%258C%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E7%258E%258B%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%259A%258A%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25AD%25B0%2F&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=34f70b89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581-%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%258D%2583%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2586%258D%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A1%2597-%25E6%258E%259B%25E7%2599%25BD%25E5%25B8%2583%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582-%25E8%2583%258C%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E7%258E%258B%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%259A%258A%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25AD%25B0%2F&h=0cb2a7e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%8